Reflection
This activity helped me understand that generative AI systems can produce outputs that are technically coherent but factually wrong. Recognising hallucinations is an important skill, especially in cybersecurity, where decisions based on incorrect AI answers could lead to misconfiguration, misunderstanding of threats, or improper remediation steps.
